issue.body:
I have a column for "status" of a record that needs to display a certain colored badge depending on that status value. Currently I am rendering that column by using the addColumn() api along with including it in the rawColumns() array. However, I cannot sort on this column. How can I accomplish this?

Here is my controller code:
```
public function index(Request $request)
{
    if ($request->ajax()) {
        $audios = $this->audio
            ->with('client')
            ->select('audios.*');

        return Datatables::of($audios)
	    ->addIndexColumn()
            ->addColumn('is_ftp', function($row) {
                return ($row->is_ftp) ? 'Yes' : 'No';
            })
            ->addColumn('status', function($row) {
                return view('admin.audios.partials.statuses', compact('row'))->render();
            })
            ->addColumn('action', function($row) {
                return view('admin.audios.partials.actions', compact('row'))->render();
            })
            ->rawColumns(['status', 'action'])
	    ->make(true);
    }
    return view('admin.audios.index');
}
```

Here is the code for my partial that is rendered by the raw column:
```
@if($row->status == 'uploaded')
    <span class="badge badge-danger">Uploaded</span>
@endif
@if($row->status == 'claimed')
    <span class="badge badge-warning">Claimed</span>
@endif
@if($row->status == 'complete')
    <span class="badge badge-success">Complete</span>
@endif
```

Here is my view code:
````
$(function () {
    let table = $('#audiosTable').DataTable({
        processing: true,
        serverSide: true,
        ajax: "{{ route('admin.audios.index') }}",
        columns: [
            {data: 'number', name: 'number'},
            {data: 'doctor_name', name: 'doctor_name'},
            {data: 'filename', name: 'filename'},
            {data: 'is_ftp', name: 'is_ftp'},
            {data: 'created_at', name: 'created_at'},
            {data: 'status', name: 'status', orderable: true},
            {data: 'action', name: 'action', orderable: false, searchable: false},
        ],
        order: [
            [0, 'desc']
        ]
    });
});
````

