```

Self-join / nested relationship is not yet fully supported. A work-around is to use [filterColumn](https://yajrabox.com/docs/laravel-datatables/10.0/filter-column). Something like:

```php
    return DataTables::eloquent($model)
                ->filterColumn('subDepartment.name', function($query, $keyword) {
                    $query->whereHas('subDepartment', fn($q) => $q->where('name', $keyword));
                })
                ->toJson();

